#: ../../source/cli/bench.rst:18
msgid "``server``"
msgstr "``server``"

#: ../../source/cli/bench.rst:19
msgid ""
"End-to-end sanity test against a running LMCache MP cache server (ZMQ + "
"HTTP). Requires the full ``lmcache`` install and a GPU."
msgstr "针对运行中的 LMCache MP 缓存服务器（ZMQ + HTTP）的端到端完整性测试。需要完整的 ``lmcache`` 安装和一个 GPU。"

#: ../../source/cli/bench.rst:21
msgid "``l2``"
msgstr "``l2``"

#: ../../source/cli/bench.rst:22
msgid ""
"Throughput / latency benchmark against an L2 cache adapter (store / "
"lookup / load)."
msgstr "针对 L2 缓存适配器的吞吐量/延迟基准测试（存储/查找/加载）。"

#: ../../source/cli/bench.rst:33
msgid "engine"
msgstr "引擎"

#: ../../source/cli/bench.rst:35
msgid ""
"The ``lmcache bench engine`` command runs sustained performance "
"benchmarks against an inference engine (e.g., vLLM). It supports multiple"
" workload types that exercise different caching patterns and reports "
"TTFT, decoding speed, and throughput metrics."
msgstr ""
"``lmcache bench engine`` 命令对推理引擎（例如 "
"vLLM）进行持续性能基准测试。它支持多种工作负载类型，以测试不同的缓存模式，并报告 TTFT、解码速度和吞吐量指标。"

#: ../../source/cli/bench.rst:44
msgid "There are three ways to configure the benchmark:"
msgstr "配置基准测试有三种方法："

#: ../../source/cli/bench.rst:46
