msgid ""
"The ``--l2-adapter`` JSON / ``L2_ADAPTER_JSON`` env var was missing or "
"could not be parsed."
msgstr "缺少或无法解析 ``--l2-adapter`` JSON / ``L2_ADAPTER_JSON`` 环境变量。"

